==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#The round disk used to play [[wink]]s in the game of [[tiddlywinks]]. It may be no smaller than 25mm (formerly 1 inch) in diameter, no greater than 51mm (formerly 2 inches) in diameter, and no greater than 5mm (formerly 3/8 inch) in thickness at its edge 
#(rare) someone who squidges a [[wink]] in the game of [[tiddlywinks]]

